sql: SELECT DISTINCT INSTRUCTORalias0.NAME FROM INSTRUCTOR AS INSTRUCTORalias0 INNER JOIN OFFERING_INSTRUCTOR AS OFFERING_INSTRUCTORalias0 ON OFFERING_INSTRUCTORalias0.INSTRUCTOR_ID = INSTRUCTORalias0.INSTRUCTOR_ID INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 ON OFFERING_INSTRUCTORalias0.OFFERING_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.OFFERING_ID INNER JOIN COURSE AS COURSEalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 ON SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER WHERE COURSEalias0.NAME LIKE "Autonomous Robotics" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "WN" AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
